org.apache.commons.functor

Interface Function<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the returned value type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Functor, NullaryFunctor
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Aggregator<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractListBackedAggregator, AbstractNoStoreAggregator, AbstractTimedAggregator, ArrayListBackedAggregator, BoundFunction, ConditionalFunction, Constant, FullyBoundFunction, PredicateFunction, ProcedureFunction, RecursiveEvaluation, TransformedFunction

    public interface Function<T>
extends NullaryFunctor
    A functor that takes no arguments and returns a value.

    Implementors are encouraged but not required to make their functors Serializable.

    1.0
